<div id="container">
<div id="slogan">start relationships without ruining friendships</div>
<h2>Step 1</h2>
<p>
	<% if !mobile_device? %>
	<%= link_to image_tag('facebook_login.png', :alt=>'Login'), '/users/auth/facebook/'%>
	<% else %>
	<%= link_to image_tag('facebook_login_small.png', :alt=>'Login'), '/users/auth/facebook/'%>
	<% end %>
</p>

<h2>Step 2</h2>
<p>Select friends you want to date. Don&#39;t worry, your friends will not know. There is also a 24 hour cooling period before we start matching you.</p>
<h2>Step 3</h2>
<p>If a friend also expresses interest in you, we will send both of you an &quot;It&#39;s a Match&quot; email. It&#39;s that simple!</p>
<h2>Step 4</h2>
<p>Spread the word through one of the social buttons below.</p>

<div class="social-button-container">
	<div class="social-button">
		<div class="g-plusone" data-size="medium"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="social-button">
    	<div class="fb-like" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/YourLocalPond" data-send="false" data-layout="button_count" data-width="450" data-show-faces="false" data-font="arial"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="social-button">
    	<a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="http://www.yourlocalpond.com" data-text="Wants to date your friends? See if they also want the same thing" data-via="YourLocalPond" data-hashtags="yourlocalpond,dating,love">Tweet</a>
	</div>
</div>

<br/><br/><br/><br/>
<%= render "shared/footer" %> 
</div>



